<p><br />To be a Peer Facilitator for this seminar, you should have a testimony of and experience in applying the principles found in the Learning Model:</p>
<ol style="list-style-type: decimal;">
<li>Exercise faith</li>
<li>Learn by the Holy Ghost</li>
<li>Lay hold on the word of God</li>
<li>Act for themselves</li>
<li>Love, serve, and teach one another</li>
</ol>
<p>You should feel comfortable facilitating and leading discussions with other students to motivate them to apply these principles in their own lives.</p>
<p><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">Qualifications</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Have the ability to teach and facilitate the learning of other students by the Spirit</li>
<li>Complete at least two semesters at BYU-Idaho prior to becoming a peer facilitator</li>
<li>Have a minimum GPA of 2.8</li>
<li>Live the BYU-Idaho Honor Code and Dress and Grooming Standards</li>
<li>No current violations with the Dean of Students office<br /><br /></li>
</ul>
<p><a href="https://cms.byui.edu/emp/sites/crawfordv/Lists/Learning%20Model%20Facilitator%20Application/Item/newifs.aspx?List=86dfce8b%2D2669%2D4b16%2D81d9%2D307827b4789b&amp;isdlg=1"><span style="font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 22px; font-size: 19px; font-weight: bold;">Apply Here</span></a></p>
<p>For quesition, email: <a href="mailto:gatewayseminars@byui.edu">gatewayseminars@byui.edu</a><strong> </strong></p>
